BlockBeats news, on October 22, according to The Data Nerd monitoring, in the past 24 hours, GSR has made multiple deposits to Binance, Bybit and Kraken:


· 250,000 ZRO (about 1.03 million US dollars) and 2.2 million ARB (about 1.33 million US dollars) were deposited in Binance;
· 12.5 million USDT were deposited in Kraken, Bybit and Binance;
· 240,000 API3 (about 437,000 US dollars) were deposited in Binance.

BlockBeats news, on October 22, 0xScope released the 2024 CEX market report, briefly summarizing the main points as follows:


· Binance is still the leader in the global centralized exchange (CEX) market, however, its market share has dropped from 51.2% to 41.68%, OKX, Bybit, Bitget have become the biggest beneficiaries of Binance's reduced market share;


· Spot trading volume: Binance's market share has decreased by 13% year-on-year but is still in the lead, and Bybit has jumped from seventh to second;


· Derivatives trading: Binance's market share fell 8.4% year-on-year, OKX, Bybit, and Bitget rose sharply;


· Platform coins: BNB dominates the market, and MNT surpasses other tokens because of its Layer-2 platform.
